snippet.title: Eggsplosion | Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Eggsplosion is a free local multiplayer party game with fighting chickens, bouncing eggs, tons of power-ups and heaps of fun.

Find Eggsplosion on the Steam store!
